items.title: Regulatory frameworks need to resemble a scaffolding, not an edifice
items.description: A regulator is expected to be an enabling force for the growth of an industry. Instead, we have created a regulatory framework which is often out of sync with reality and an obstacle to the progress of firms

items.title: New BIMA-ASBA framework could declutter unclaimed amounts with insurance companies
items.description: The new guidelines effective from March 1, 2025, state that only the necessary premium amount will be blocked and debited once the policy is issued.
